OL,3,CHome Secretary commits to Hillsborough
OL,4,CLaw but unable to give timeframe
OL,6,FYvette Cooper told ITV Granada
OL,7,FPolitical Correspondent: "The
OL,8,FHillsborough Law is something we've
OL,9,Fcommitted to for a long time. We will
OL,10,Fbe introducing a Hillsborough Law.
OL,12,FWhen pushed about about when the law
OL,13,Fmight arrive, she said: "We'll bring
OL,14,Fforward legislation, we've committed
OL,15,Fto bringing forward the Hillsborough
OL,16,FLaw. We've seen too often in the past
OL,17,Fwhere organisations and instituions
OL,18,Fhave tried to protect themselves
OL,19,Frather than the public. We need that
OL,20,Fduty of candour in place."
