OL,6,FLast week it was reported that a
OL,7,Fmeeting between Sir Keir and
OL,8,Fcampaigners had been cancelled, with
OL,9,Fclaims officials were attempting to
OL,10,Fhave the contents of a bill watered
OL,11,Fdown.
OL,13,FIt is understood concerns relate to
OL,14,Fwho the duty of candour would apply to.
OL,16,FCharlotte Hennessy, who lost her
OL,17,Ffather James in the disaster, said
OL,18,Ffamilies will hold the government to
OL,19,Faccount over any further delays.
