OL,3,CHome Secretary commits to Hillsborough
OL,4,CLaw but unable to give timeframe
OL,6,FEarlier on Thursday, Leader of the
OL,7,FHouse of Commons Lucy Powell told MPs
OL,8,Fthat the Government will take
OL,9,F"whatever time is necessary" to
OL,10,Fdeliver a Hillsborough Law to prevent
OL,11,Fcover-ups by public bodies which
OL,12,F"meets the expectations" of the
OL,13,Ffamilies.
OL,15,FBut when challenged on the whereabouts
OL,16,Fof the legislation, she said ministers
OL,17,Fare working on the proposals "at pace"
OL,18,Fand the "very worst thing" they can do
OL,19,Fis "to not meet those expectations" of
OL,20,Fthe Hillsborough families.
