OL,6,FThe Bill is expected to create a legal
OL,7,Fduty of candour on public authorities
OL,8,Fand officials to tell the truth and
OL,9,Fproactively co-operate with official
OL,10,Finvestigations and inquiries.
OL,12,FNinety-seven football fans died as a
OL,13,Fresult of a crush at the FA Cup semi-
OL,14,Ffinal between Liverpool and Nottingham
OL,15,FForest at Hillsborough Stadium in
OL,16,FSheffield.
OL,18,FThey were unlawfully killed amid a
OL,19,Fnumber of police errors, an inquest
OL,20,Fjury ruled in 2016.
