OL,6,FSurvivors and the families of the 97
OL,7,Ffans who lost their lives have been
OL,8,Finvolved in a lengthy campaign in
OL,9,Fpursuit of justice.
OL,11,FSpeaking at business questions,
OL,12,FLiberal Democrats Commons leader Marie
OL,13,FGoldman said: "On April 15, we will be
OL,14,Fmarking the 36th anniversary of the
OL,15,FHillsborough disaster and remember the
OL,16,F97 people who tragically lost their
OL,17,Flife on that dark day, as well as
OL,18,Ftheir families' subsequent fight for
OL,19,Fjustice.
