OL,6,F"Last September, the Prime Minister
OL,7,Fmade a commitment that the
OL,8,FHillsborough law would be introduced
OL,9,Fin Parliament before we reached this
OL,10,Fanniversary.
OL,12,F"A duty of candour for public servants
OL,13,Fand public bodies is long overdue. It
OL,14,Fwill help stop future cover-ups and
OL,15,Fit's vital that the legislation
OL,16,Fdelivers on the commitments made to
OL,17,FHillsborough families in a meaningful
OL,18,Fway.
