OL,6,FMs Powell replied: "As we approach the
OL,7,Fanniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,8,Ftragedy we should remember the 97
OL,9,Flives lost, all the families affected,
OL,10,Fbut also the years and years of
OL,11,Ffighting for justice and for
OL,12,Faccountability that the families have
OL,13,Fthen suffered since, frankly in the
OL,14,Fface of the state in most cases,
OL,15,Ffighting against them, and that's
OL,16,Fsomething that we should all endeavour
OL,17,Fto put right.
