OL,6,F"And as she says, the Prime Minister
OL,7,Fand the Government ` the whole
OL,8,FGovernment, myself included ` we
OL,9,Fremain focused on fulfilling our
OL,10,Fcommitment to the Hillsborough
OL,11,Ffamilies on bringing forward and
OL,12,Fenacting a 'Hillsborough Law' which of
OL,13,Fcourse includes, as she says, a duty
OL,14,Fof candour at all times, a very
OL,15,Fimportant measure to take forward.
OL,17,F"But I think the most important issue
OL,18,Fat this time is to ensure that the
OL,19,Flegislation reflects the full range of
OL,20,Fconcerns and experiences, and meets
OL,21,Fthe expectations of the families.
