OL,4,CLaw but unable to give timeframe
OL,6,F"I think the very worst thing we can
OL,7,Fdo at this point in time is to not
OL,8,Fmeet those expectations when all of
OL,9,Fthe trust and issues there are about
OL,10,Fthe state failing to live up to those
OL,11,Fexpectations of the families.
OL,13,F"So we are working on the Bill at
OL,14,Fpace, but we will take whatever time
OL,15,Fis necessary to work collaboratively
OL,16,Fwith the families and their
OL,17,Frepresentatives, because getting that
OL,18,Flegislation right is actually our
OL,19,Foverwhelming priority at this time,
OL,20,FI'm sure she can understand that."
